    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And Rehoboam took him Mahalath, the daughter of Jerimoth, the son of David, to wife,.... Of which son of David we nowhere else read; perhaps he might be the son of one of his concubines, or he might have two names: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Abihail the daughter of Eliab the son of Jesse; who was David's eldest brother. 1 Samuel 17:13. She must be a granddaughter or great-granddaughter of his. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and Abihail the daughter of Eliab the son of Jesse; who was David's eldest brother. ",
            "children": []
